{"tid":719383,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣可以感動到另一半","createTime":"2018-06-27T11:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T13:12:56.000Z","uid":27969,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ad6fa1b42fc5dcf35645bf1023b3e7bf374da85f","tid":719383,"uid":27969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:20:53.000Z","msg":"早幾日同男朋友嘈交 佢同我講大家要冷靜一排<br />\n仲要唔知冷靜幾耐<br />\n佢話因為我做嘅野 搞到佢冇咗樣野<br />\n話冷靜緊依段時間 佢都會係我身邊<br />\n話都需要一個人陪佢傾計<br />\n我以為我可以慢慢move on到 日頭都還可以 <br />\n一到夜晚個人就好亂 會諗好想同返佢一齊<br />\n我係咪真係冇任何方法一齊返？<br />\n佢嚟緊生日 我好想佢生日個陣 可以同佢好返<br />\n當然依啲只係我ff <br />\n我唔知可以再做啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4947c96e55bb9256437f04b75e91e12395c0972","tid":719383,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:32:49.000Z","msg":"冷靜又會傾計，咁就唔叫冷靜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50781d6e6ed28e240fff86891b6afde6df09c3f6","tid":719383,"uid":27969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4947c96e55bb9256437f04b75e91e12395c0972","tid":719383,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:32:49.000Z","msg":"冷靜又會傾計，咁就唔叫冷靜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"咁叫啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女兵？"},{"pid":"3c8de3163171b958e986e2dc06febbcaca3fb552","tid":719383,"uid":23590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:38:43.000Z","msg":"可唔可以詳細啲講你做咗啲咩 令到佢點"},{"pid":"fbbf1bbdf4c3b03e5c7f5cbe43fc4a298da4b091","tid":719383,"uid":92603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:40:05.000Z","msg":"有冇試過幫佢含?"},{"pid":"aaa0d8169b8f8e0ebac7111b8c902bd4bf57eb0c","tid":719383,"uid":27969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"